This package provides the functions for signal identification of IMFs from noise-assisted MEMD.
Further questions, please contact vhumeng@gmail.com or hualou.liang@drexel.edu.

To reproduce the figures in the paper below under submission, run demo.m

Meng Hu and Hualou Liang, Search for information-bearing components in
neural data, PLoS ONE, 2014, submitted.

